Most probably List&lt;Invoice&gt; is not what you want to put into the Exchange. I assume you want output XML to be something like:
```
&lt;Invoices&gt;
 &lt;Invoice&gt;...&lt;/Invoice&gt;
 &lt;Invoice&gt;...&lt;/Invoice&gt;
 ...
&lt;/Invoices&gt;
```

in which case it&#39;s probably most straightforward to declare a container class:

```
@XmlRootElement
public class Invoices {
  private List&lt;Invoice&gt; invoices;
}
```

(getter and setter omitted).

Then generate your schema and put this ```Invoices``` object into the Exchange.

