I figure this out, hope this is a good solution.
I put the `Query` inside off the `addListener`. And now it works. 


    databaseUsers.child(userID).addListenerForSingleValueEvent(new ValueEventListener() {
            @Override
            public void onDataChange(@NonNull DataSnapshot snapshot) {

                Users userprofile = snapshot.getValue(Users.class);

                if (userprofile != null) {

                    String user = userprofile.getUserStorage();

