Look at your loop:

    for (int i = 0; i &lt; list1.getSize(); i++){
        website = list1.getElementAt(i);
        username = list1.getElementAt(i);
        password = list1.getElementAt(i);
        upInfo.add(new UsernamesAndPasswords(website, username, password));
