_driver is a variable of IWebDriver before use you have to initiate it e.g ```IWebDriver _driver = new ChromeDriver();``` 
```
_driver.SelectDropDownByText(
                clickId:&quot;EnterOrderModel.reportstoprofs_B-1&quot;,
